    <entry>
      <title>Systemctl管理Springboot Jar包</title>
      <link href="/2018/09/06/2018%20Systemctl%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86Springboot%20Jar%E5%8C%85/"/>
      <url>/2018/09/06/2018%20Systemctl%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86Springboot%20Jar%E5%8C%85/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="增加服务文件"><a href="#增加服务文件" class="headerlink" title="增加服务文件"></a>增加服务文件</h3><p>进入服务文件目录：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /etc/systemd/system/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建服务文件：（文件名对应项目名，可自定义）</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim my-apps.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a> <h3 id="编辑内容"><a href="#编辑内容" class="headerlink" title="编辑内容"></a>编辑内容</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[Unit]</span><br><span class="line">Description=apps</span><br><span class="line">After=syslog.target</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[Service]</span><br><span class="line">ExecStart=/usr/software/jdk1.8.0_131/bin/java -jar /var/apps/my-apps.jar</span><br><span class="line">Restart=always</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[Install]</span><br><span class="line">WantedBy=multi-user.target</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其它项目使用只要修改 <code>Description</code> 和 <code>ExecStart</code> 即可。</p><h3 id="服务操作"><a href="#服务操作" class="headerlink" title="服务操作"></a>服务操作</h3><h4 id="启动服务"><a href="#启动服务" class="headerlink" title="启动服务"></a>启动服务</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl start my-apps.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="停止服务"><a href="#停止服务" class="headerlink" title="停止服务"></a>停止服务</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl stop my-apps.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="服务状态"><a href="#服务状态" class="headerlink" title="服务状态"></a>服务状态</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl status my-apps.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="开机启动"><a href="#开机启动" class="headerlink" title="开机启动"></a>开机启动</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> my-apps.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="开机禁用"><a href="#开机禁用" class="headerlink" title="开机禁用"></a>开机禁用</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">disable</span> my-apps.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="查看服务是否开机启动"><a href="#查看服务是否开机启动" class="headerlink" title="查看服务是否开机启动"></a>查看服务是否开机启动</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl is-enabled my-apps.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="项目日志"><a href="#项目日志" class="headerlink" title="项目日志"></a>项目日志</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">journalctl -u my-apps.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
